Amaka Gessler (a mụrụ  ya na 24 April 1990) bụ onye New Zealand nnọchiteanya na-egwu mmiri
O ritere nrite ọla ọcha na 4 × 200 m freestyle relay n'afo 2010 Commonwealth  ya na  Lauren Boyle, Natasha Hind na Penelope Marshall
O meriri  ọla nchara otu  na 4 × 100 m freestyle relay na otu egwuregwu
Ọ nọchitere anya New Zealand na egwuregwu n'afo 2012 nke Olimpik  4 × 200 m na 4 × 100 m Freestyle relay
